I think we'll wrap it up here.

00:46:27.880 --> 00:46:29.260
Thank you all for coming.

00:46:29.260 --> 00:46:31.860
Thank you, Dr. Adam
Kucharski, for being here.

00:46:31.860 --> 00:46:33.010
It was a pleasure.

00:46:33.010 --> 00:46:33.790
Thank you so much.

